 seek feedback from your\nteam mates. It must include questions on believability and style.</font></font></font></p>',1,'uploadsingle',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2097152,1137922800,0,10,1125830214),(92,12,'Extension Task','<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span>Use\nthe feedback to improve your website.</span></font></font></p>',1,'uploadsingle',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,1024000,0,0,0,1125830257),(93,12,'Task 1 ? Heroes and Villains','<div style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: left;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><b>(i)</b>	Design\na database to hold all of the information, it will need sections for\nname, age, last known location and 4 more facts that you can choose\nyourself, make sure you have space for the pictures.</font></font></p><div style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: left;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><b>(ii)</b>	Design\na form that will let you access all of the data.</font></font></p><div style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: left;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><b>(iii)	</b>Research\nand gather information on fictional heroes and villains, you will\nneed facts and a photo of each.</font></font></p><div style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: left;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><b>(iv)</b>	Produce\na table to show where you got your information from, it should look\nlike the one below:</font></font></p><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\n</div><table width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"4\" bordercolor=\"#000000\" border=\"1\" style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: auto;\">\n	<col wid