font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">Network\n				Card</font></font></p>\n			</td>\n			<td width=\"50%\">\n				<p><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">Scanner</font></font></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr valign=\"top\">\n			<td width=\"50%\">\n				<p><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">CD\n				rom</font></font></p>\n			</td>\n			<td width=\"50%\">\n				<p><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">Floppy\n				drive</font></font></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in;\"><br />\n</p>',1,'uploadsingle',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2097152,1139737200,0,10,1125831028),(99,12,'Extension Task','<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: left;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span>Add\n the following items to your database: TV capture card, USB port,\nScsi port, projector ,  DVD drive, CDRW</span></font></font></p>',1,'uploadsingle',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,1024000,0,0,0,1125831098),(100,12,'Homework','<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: left;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\"><span>Find\nthree computer quotes from a magazine or newspaper. Cut out the\nquotes and add them to a report saying what each quote has top offer,\nand which is the best value for money, with reasons.</span></font></font></p>',1,'uploadsingle',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,1024000,0,0,0,1125831135),(101,12,'Task 4 ? Capture Gates','<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: left;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><b>(i)</b>	Use\nthe map to find where Dr Gates is hiding, a clue is given below.</font></font></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: left;\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><b>(ii)</b><span>	Draw\nan arrow onto the map where you think the hiding place is</span></font></font></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: left;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><b>(iii)</b>	Add\nthis map to your Heroes and villains database.<br /></font></font></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><img width=\"664\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" height=\"540\" border=\"0\" src=\"/moodle/file.php/12/map.png\" alt=\"map\" title=\"map\" /></font></font><br /></div>\n	\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: left;\">You must work as a\nteam to find out his location, a clue below has been given in binary,\nyou must go to <a href=\"http://nickciske.com/tools/binary.php\">http://nickciske.com/tools/binary.php</a>\nto decode it.</p>\n\n\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">The code is:<br /></div><p style=\"margin-left: 2.04in; margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: center;\"><b>01000100		    00110100	</b></p>\n<br /><br />',1,'uploadsingle',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2097152,1140946800,0,10,1125831508),(102,12,'Extension Task','<p align=\"left\" style=\"margin-left: -0.01in; margin-bottom: 0in;\">\n<font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">Find\nout what the following numbers are in binary: 1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8. Put\nthis information into a table and save its as binary numbers.</font></font></p>\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"margin-left: -0.01in; margin-bottom: 0in;\">\n<br />\n</p>',1,'uploadsingle',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,1024000,0,0,0,1125831613),(103,12,'Task 1 ? Design in Progress','<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: left;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"3\"><b><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">(i)</font>	</b><span><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">\nCreate an action plan to show you what you will be doing and in what\norder, if you are working in a team, you must also include a section\nfor job allocation. </font></span>	</font></font></p><