sp;</div><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: left;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><b>(i)</b>	As\na team give your presentation to the rest of the class. This should\nlast for at least 5 minutes.</font></font></p><div style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: left;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><b>(ii)</b>	Evaluate\nhow well you thought your presentation went using the following\ncriteria:</font></font></p><div style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: left;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">Length\nof presentation</font></font></p><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\n</div><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: left;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">What\nwas in the presentation</font></font></p><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\n</div><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: left;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">What\nyou didn\'t like about it</font></font></p><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\n</div><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: left;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">What\nyou did like about it</font></font></p><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\n</div><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: left;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">What\ncould be improved</font></font></p>',1,'uploadsingle',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2097152,1153215600,0,10,1125833078),(107,12,'Homework','<font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\"><span>Write\na letter to a friend using the skills you have learnt. Remember to use formatting techniques to produce a letter similar to the example. ieTab &amp; Return.</span></font></font>',1,'upload