o one with the website you have at\n				the moment! Use the following devices to create one that looks\n				more realistic.....</font></font></p>\n				<ul><p align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0in;\" /></ul>\n				<p align=\"right\"><font color=\"#ff0000\"><font face=\"Bitstream Vera Serif\"><font size=\"3\"><b>*\n				End of Message *</b></font></font></font></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	\n</tbody></table>\n</p><div style=\"text-align: left;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">(iv)</span> Use\nthe following devices to make your website more professional:</span></font></font><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: left;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">Scanner<br /><br /></font></font></div><div style=\"text-align: left;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">Digital\nCamera</font></font><br /></div><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: left;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">Microphone</font></font></p>\n\n<p>\n</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in;\"><br />\n</p>\n<p />',0,12,0,0,0,'assignment',89,'due',1137318000,0,1,'',1,1139337590,NULL),(90,'Homework','<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: left;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\"><span>Produce\na report stating what the following common file formats are for, and\nwhat their advantages are: bmp, png, pcx,  gif, jpeg, mpg, avi. Use a\ntable to show your results</span></font></font></p>',0,12,0,0,0,'assignment',90,'due',1137318000,0,1,'',1,1139337590,NULL),(91,'Task 3 ? Feedback','<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"4\" style=\"font-size: 15pt;\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><b>(i)</b>	Produce\na questionnaire with at least 10 questions to seek feedback from your\nteam mates. It must include questions on believability and style.</font></font></font></p>',0,12,0,0,0,'assignment',91,'due',1137922800,0,1,'',1,1139337590,NULL),(92,'Extension Task','<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span>Use\nthe feedback to improve your website.</span></font></font></p>',0,12,0,0,0,'assignment',92,'due',0,0,1,'',1,1139337590,NULL),(93,'Task 1 ? Heroes and Villains','<div style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: left;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><b>(i)</b>	Design\na database to hold all of the information, it will need sections for\nname, age, last known location and 4 more facts that you can choose\nyourself, make sure you have space for the pictures.</font></font></p><div style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: left;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><b>(ii)</b>	Design\na form that will let you access all of the data.</font></font></p><div style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: left;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><b>(iii)	</b>Research\nand gather information on fictional heroes and villains, you will\nneed facts and a photo of each.</font></font></p><div style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: left;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><b>(iv)</b>	Produce\na table to show where you got your information from, it should look\nlike the one below:</font></font></p><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\n</div><table width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"4\" bordercolor=\"#000000\" border=\"1\" style=\"text-align: left; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: auto;\">\n	<col width=\"51*\" />\n	<col width=\"51*\" />\n	<col width=\"154*\" />\n	<thead>\n		<tr valign=\"top\">\n			<th width=\"20%\">\n				<p style=\"font-style: normal;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><b>Name\n				of website</b></font></font></p>\n			</th>\n			<th width=\"20%\">\n				<p style=\"font-style: normal;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><b>Website\n				Topic</b></font></font></p>\n			</th>\n			<th width=\"60%\">\n				<p style=\"font-style: normal;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><b>Types\n				of information used</b></font></font></p>\n			</th>\n		</tr>\n	</thead>\n	<tbody>\n		<tr valign=\"top\">\n			<td width=\"20%\">\n				<p style=\"font-style: normal;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">Superheroes.com</font></font></p>\n			</td>\n			<td width=\"20%\">\n				<p style=\"font-style: normal;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">All\n				about superheroes</font></font></p>\n			</td>\n			<td width=\"60%\">\n				<p style=\"font-style: normal;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">I\n				got pictures and text from this website</font></font></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\n</div><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: left;\"><br />\n</p>',0,12,0,0,0,'assignment',93,'due',1138527600,0,1,'',1,1139337590,NULL),(94,'Extension Task','<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: left;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">Add\na section to your database which will show pictures where your\nvillains have last been sighted.</font></font></p>',0,12,0,0,0,'assignment',94,'due',0,0,1,'',1,1139337590,NULL),(95,'Homework','<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: left;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\"><span>Create\na practise database to store the information on your music collection</span></font></font></p>',0,12,0,0,0,'assignment',95,'due',0,0,1,'',1,1139337590,NULL),(96,'Task 2 ? H.O.L.M.E.S','<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><b>(i)</b>	Produce\na series of queries to turn your database into a crime lookup tool.\nThis should let a user search your database for villains or super\nheroes.</font></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in;\"><br />\n</p>',0,12,0,0,0,'assignment',96,'due',0,0,1,'',1,1139337590,NULL),(97,'Homework','<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\"><span>Create\nqueries for your music database</span></font></font></p>',0,12,0,0,0,'assignment',97,'due',0,0,1,'',1,1139337590,NULL),(98,'Task 3 ? Computer Parts','<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: left;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><b>(i)</b>	Decide\nwhat fields need to be used in your new database</font></font></p><div style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: left;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><b>(ii)</b>	Design\na database to hold all of the information, it should have section for\nname of component,  size, price and a section for any other\ninformation.</font></font></p><div style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: left;\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><b>(iii)	</b><span>Research\ndifferent types of hardware, make sure its the most expensive you can\nfind, as the super computer won\'t be cheap. </span></font></font>\n</p><div style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: left;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">Your\ndatabase will need to include information on the following computer\nparts:</font></font></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in;\"><br />\n</p>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"4\" bordercolor=\"#000000\" border=\"1\">\n	<col width=\"128*\" />\n	<col width=\"128*\" />\n	<thead>\n		<tr valign=\"top\">\n			<td width=\"50%\">\n				<p><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">CPU\n				(Processor)</font></font></p>\n			</td>\n			<td width=\"50%\">\n				<p><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">Sound\n				Card</font></font></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</thead>\n	<tbody>\n		<tr valign=\"top\">\n			<td width=\"50%\">\n				<p><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">Memory</font></font></p>\n			</td>\n			<td width=\"50%\">\n				<p><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">Keyboard</font></font></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr valign=\"top\">\n			<td width=\"50%\">\n				<p><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">Motherboard</font></font></p>\n			</td>\n			<td width=\"50%\">\n				<p><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">Monitor</font></font></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr valign=\"top\">\n			<td width=\"50%\">\n				<p><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">Hard\n				Drive</font></font></p>\n			</td>\n			<td width=\"50%\">\n				<p><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">Mouse</font></font></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr valign=\"top\">\n			<td width=\"50%\">\n				<p><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">Video\n				Card</font></font></p>\n			</td>\n			<td width=\"50%\">\n				<p><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">Printer</font></font></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr valign=\"top\">\n			<td width=\"50%\">\n				<p><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">Network\n				Card</font></font></p>\n			</td>\n			<td width=\"50%\">\n				<p><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">Scanner</font></font></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr valign=\"top\">\n			<td width=\"50%\">\n				<p><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">CD\n				rom</font></font></p>\n			</td>\n			<td width=\"50%\">\n				<p><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">Floppy\n				drive</font></font></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in;\"><br />\n</p>',0,12,0,0,0,'assignment',98,'due',1139737200,0,1,'',1,1139337590,NULL),(99,'Extension Task','<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: left;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span>Add\n the following items to your database: TV capture card, USB port,\nScsi port, projector ,  DVD drive, CDRW</span></font></font></p>',0,12,0,0,0,'assignment',99,'due',0,0,1,'',1,1139337590,NULL),(100,'Homework','<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: left;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\"><span>Find\nthree computer quotes from a magazine or newspaper. Cut out the\nquotes and add them to a report saying what each quote has top offer,\nand which is the best value for money, with reasons.</span></font></font></p>',0,12,0,0,0,'assignment',100,'due',0,0,1,'',1,1139337590,NULL),(101,'Task 4 ? Capture Gates','<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: left;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><b>(i)</b>	Use\nthe map to find where Dr Gates is hiding, a clue is given below.</font></font></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: left;\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><b>(ii)</b><span>	Draw\nan arrow onto the map where you think the hiding place is</span></font></font></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: left;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><b>(iii)</b>	Add\nthis map to your Heroes and villains database.<br /></font></font></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><img width=\"664\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" height=\"540\" border=\"0\" src=\"/moodle/file.php/12/map.png\" alt=\"map\" title=\"map\" /></font></font><br /></div>\n	\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: left;\">You must work as a\nteam to find out his location, a clue below has been given in binary,\nyou must go to <a href=\"http://nickciske.com/tools/binary.php\">http://nickciske.com/tools/binary.php</a>\nto decode it.</p>\n\n\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">The code is:<br /></div><p style=\"margin-left: 2.04in; margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: center;\"><b>01000100		    00110100	</b></p>\n<br /><br />',0,12,0,0,0,'assignment',101,'due',1140946800,0,1,'',1,1139337590,NULL),(102,'Extension Task','<p align=\"left\" style=\"margin-left: -0.01in; margin-bottom: 0in;\">\n<font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">Find\nout what the following numbers are in binary: 1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8. Put\nthis information into a table and save its as binary numbers.</font></font></p>\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"margin-left: -0.01in; margin-bottom: 0in;\">\n<br />\n</p>',0,12,0,0,0,'assignment',102,'due',0,0,1,'',1,1139337590,NULL),(103,'Task 1 ? Design in Progress','<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: left;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"3\"><b><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">(i)</font>	</b><span><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">\nCreate an action plan to show you what you will be doing and in what\norder, if you are working in a team, you must also include a section\nfor job allocation. </font></span>	</font></font></p><div style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: left;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><b>(ii)</b>	Produce\na plan for the pages, it must show where everything will be placed,\nincluding pictures, title, text,  and should have a \'key\' for the\ncolours used.</font></font></p><div style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: left;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><b>(iii)</b>	Produce\na time line which which shows the timing of your presentation and\nwhere different members of your team will be speaking.</font></font></p>',0,12,0,0,0,'assignment',103,'due',0,0,1,'',1,1139337590,NULL),(104,'Task 2 ? Producing the Goods','<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: left;\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><b>(i)	</b><span>Design\na presentation to show the new recruits, it must have at least 10\nslides and be over 5 minutes long. You must work as a team.</span></font></font></p><div style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: left;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><b>(ii)</b>	Write\na section to speak in front of the new recruits while the slide show\nis going on, it should cover what they are viewing on the screen,\nthis is a team project so you must choose between you who wants to\ntalk about what and in what order.</font></font></p>',0,12,0,0,0,'assignment',104,'due',1118482800,0,1,'',1,1139337590,NULL),(105,'Extension Task','<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: left;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\"><span>Produce\na brief presentation about your favourite hobby</span></font></font></p>',0,12,0,0,0,'assignment',105,'due',0,0,1,'',1,1139337590,NULL),(106,'Task 3 ? Impressing the new Recruits','<div style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: left;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><b>(i)</b>	As\na team give your presentation to the rest of the class. This should\nlast for at least 5 minutes.</font></font></p><div style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: left;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><b>(ii)</b>	Evaluate\nhow well you thought your presentation went using the following\ncriteria:</font></font></p><div style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: left;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">Length\nof presentation</font></font></p><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\n</div><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: left;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">What\nwas in the presentation</font></font></p><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\n</div><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: left;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">What\nyou didn\'t like about it</font></font></p><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\n</div><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: left;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">What\nyou did like about it</font></font></p><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\n</div><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: left;\"><font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\" style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">What\ncould be improved</font></font></p>',0,12,0,0,0,'assignment',106,'due',1153215600,0,1,'',1,1139337590,NULL),(107,'Homework','<font face=\"Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"2\"><span>Write\na letter to a friend using the skills you have learnt. Remember to use formatting techniques to produce a letter similar to the example. ieTab &amp; Return.</span></font></font>',0,12,0,0,0,'assignment',107,'due',1127390700,0,1,'',1,1139337590,NULL);
